overview: Three-time Latin Grammy nominee Miguel Bosé celebrates 30 years of making music in a landmark concert held in Spain's Plaza de Toros de las Ventas. With the help of special guest artists Alaska, Bimba Bose, Rafa Sanchez and Ana Torroja, the Panamanian-born singer plows through a set list of his most beloved and popular songs, including a pair of hit singles from his 2007 album "Papito": "Morena Mia" and "Nena."
title: Miguel Bosé: Papitour
